Package: Friedman
Title: Simple Visualization Wrappers for Exploratory Data Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Animesh", "Singh", email = "animesh664@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Animesh Singh [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Animesh Singh <animesh664@gmail.com>
Description: A small set of wrapper functions around ggplot2 and lattice for
    quickly making common plots like histograms, scatter plots, and box plots.
